## FE Integration (Zero Code Changes)

The existing FE drag-and-drop priority system works automatically:

1. **Seed data** adds 2 rows to `objective_weights` table
2. `constraints_v2_seed_data.sql` auto-populates `objective_priorities` via existing `INSERT ... SELECT` pattern
3. UPDATE places both in "medium" priority bucket (positions 4, 5)
4. FE fetches `GET /objective-priorities/` which JOINs both tables â€” new objectives appear as draggable cards
5. User drags cards between High/Medium/Low â€” `PUT /objective-priorities/{id}` recalculates `weight_coefficient`
6. Solver reads `GET /objective-weights/` on next run â€” picks up updated weights

